# Objective Brief — G&I Strategic Vision Presentation

## What is this presentation?
An inspirational and strategic session from G&I (Growth & Innovation) to the CEO Global of Alkemy Group. It is NOT a status report, NOT a budget request, NOT an operational review. It is the tip of the spear that will define where Alkemy Spain goes commercially.

The goal: **get Duccio to buy into the vision** — to see that G&I has a clear direction, a competent team, and a plan worth backing. If he buys the idea, we work the budget with Diego afterwards.

